    "description": "DeltaCrypt FIPS Module v1.0.0.0 is a software module providing cryptographic functionality implemented in DeltaCrypt Encryption Applications that complies with FIPS 140-2 level 1 requirements. DeltaCrypt FIPS Module provides data encryption for DeltaCrypt applications protecting files and folders on computer hard disks, mobile data, CD-ROMs and DVDs. It also ensures data protection of removable drives used in combination with DeltaCrypt Mobile Device Control which controls removable drives used on a network, offers audit and tracking capabilities as well as threat detection and policy",
